.TH GB-PROXY 1 "July 2026" "GB-proxy 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
gb-proxy \- adapt modern web content for legacy web clients
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B gb-proxy
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B gb-proxy
is an extensible HTTP proxy for GEOBENCH and other constrained legacy web
clients.  It simplifies HTML, rewrites links, and converts images into formats
supported by early computers.
.PP
The packaged systemd service listens only on the loopback interface by default.
Edit
.I /etc/sysconfig/gb-proxy
before exposing it to a trusted LAN.  The proxy is not intended to be exposed
directly to the public Internet.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI "--config " PATH
Load the Python configuration file at
.IR PATH .
.TP
.BI "--host " ADDRESS
Listen on
.IR ADDRESS .
The default is 127.0.0.1.
.TP
.BI "--port " PORT
Listen on
.IR PORT .
The default is 5001.
.TP
.BI "--advertise-host " HOST
Use
.I HOST
or an absolute HTTP URL when generating proxy links returned to clients.
.TP
.BI "--cache-dir " PATH
Store disposable converted resources under
.IR PATH .
.TP
.BI "--state-dir " PATH
Store persistent runtime state under
.IR PATH .
.TP
.BI "--threads " COUNT
Run the Waitress server with
.I COUNT
worker threads.  The default is one.  GB-proxy uses one process, and several
bundled extensions hold process-global conversation or override state; keep one
thread when using those extensions.
.TP
.B --check-config
Validate the selected configuration and exit without starting the server.
.TP
.B --version
Print the program version and exit.
.TP
.BR -h ", " --help
Show command-line help and exit.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B GB_PROXY_CONFIG
Configuration path used when
.B --config
is not supplied.
.TP
.B GB_PROXY_HOST
Default listening address.
.TP
.B GB_PROXY_PORT
Default listening port.
.TP
.B GB_PROXY_CACHE_DIR
Default cache directory.
.TP
.B GB_PROXY_STATE_DIR
Default state directory.
.TP
.B GB_PROXY_ADVERTISE_HOST
Default host or HTTP URL used in generated proxy links.
.TP
.B GB_PROXY_THREADS
Default number of Waitress threads.
.TP
.B GB_PROXY_LOG_LEVEL
Python logging level.  The default is INFO.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /etc/gb-proxy/config.py
System configuration file.
.TP
.I /etc/sysconfig/gb-proxy
Service command-line settings.
.TP
.I /var/cache/gb-proxy
Packaged service cache directory.
.TP
.I /var/lib/gb-proxy
Packaged service state directory.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR systemctl (1),
.BR systemd.service (5)
